Author: ggforestplotR Authors [aut, cre]
Maintainer: ggforestplotR Authors <dev@example.com>
Description: Tools for turning model coefficients into flexible forest
    plots using ggplot2. The package provides helpers to standardize
    coefficient data from a range of modelling workflows and render
    publication-ready coefficient plots with a consistent interface.
